## Routing Standard

All task routing follows the master router config at:
`/Users/elbarrio/.openclaw/workspace/adolfo-router.yaml`

Key rules:
- Classify every task (type / complexity 1–5 / risk) before dispatching
- Activate minimum agent set only — never fan out to all agents
- Complexity 1–2 → local (Haiku until Ollama configured); 3 → Haiku; 4–5 → Sonnet
- Mandatory Sonnet for: legal, code, financial decisions, strategic planning, client-facing deliverables
- Context firewall: 1500 token cap, semantic retrieval (top 3), no raw doc dumps
- Night Mode (22:00–06:00): batch on cheap models, Sonnet review at 08:00
- El Pibe owns all logging — one shared summary per task
